{
  "texts": [
    "Thoughtful translation is essential, but implementation science provides proven guidance.The time for debate has passed.",
    "Patients worldwide stand to benefit, and responsible leaders must act urgently.",
    "Strategic pilots, iterative scaling and governance emphasizing ethics alongside innovation will realize long-overdue progress.",
    "Generative AI cannot single-handedly fix broken systems, but carefully facilitated adoption can catalyse reform while upholding healthcare's humanitarian obligations.",
    "The approach, not just technology, defines success."
  ]
}